# English only

- All user-visible UI copy, validation messages, API JSON messages, and emails must be written in **English**.
- Code identifiers (classes, methods, variables, routes, config keys), database seed text, migrations comments if any, commit messages, and `README` must use **English**.
- Do not add Portuguese (or other non-English) strings to the codebase, tests, or documentation files in this repository.
